flavor_text_entries.red:
Its hard scales
provide strong
protection. It uses its hefty
bulk to execute
powerful moves.
flavor_text_entries.blue:
Its hard scales
provide strong
protection. It uses its hefty
bulk to execute
powerful moves.
flavor_text_entries.yellow:
Tough scales cover
the sturdy body
of this POKéMON. It appears that
the scales grow
in cycles.
flavor_text_entries.gold:
Its body is cover­
ed with needle-
like scales. It never shows signs
of shrinking from
any attack.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
It uses its scaly,
rugged body to
seal the entrance of its nest and
protect its young
from predators.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
The hard scales
that cover its
strong body serve as excellent
protection from
any attack.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
NIDOQUEEN’s body is encased in
extremely hard scales. It is adept at
sending foes flying with harsh tackles. This POKéMON is at its strongest when
it is defending its young.

flavor_text_entries.sword:
Nidoqueen is better at defense than offense.
With scales like armor, this Pokémon will shield
its children from any kind of attack.
flavor_text_entries.shield:
It pacifies offspring by placing them in the gaps
between the spines on its back. The spines will
never secrete poison while young are present.
